message: Undid revision 736825862 by [[Special:Contributions/Sro23|Sro23]] ([[User talk:Sro23|talk]]) Do not blanket-undo my changes because you are having an un-related edit-war with a troll. I have valid justification and you have provided none.

No such political or socio-economic system where White people are at an advantage has been identified and has only been 'supposed' to exist. There is no citation or reference for the sentence it is mentioned in, so it cannot remain and presented as fact.

Undid revision. There is no factual or proven 'dominant' white culture or even a definition for such a term. The reference cited only refers to the United States and has nothing to do with Black pride in Europe, Africa or elsewhere.
Edited definition to match that of Black supremacy page. Removed unsourced claim regarding political and socio-economic ideology. Edited with the aim of making each opening statements unbiased..
/* Africa and global markets */  This important historical and economic claim could have seemingly been plucked out of the air. Detrimental to leave this in without evidence.

/* The end of the war */ I feel as though this entire section is unneeded, poorly written and extremely opinionated. While I have no intention of removing such a massive block of text I have instead decided to remove the most opinionated claims.
